A giant panda is pictured enjoying a shower at Beijing Zoo on May 23, 2019 as the temperature in the city climbed up to 37 degree Celsius, the highest of the year so far. The zoo showers the Panda or sprays its house regularly to help the animal cope with the hot weather. (Photo: China News Service)  

